  <title>Resizing and Orienting the Ruler</title>

  <media type="image" src="figures/size.png">
    <p>Changing the ruler's dimension and orientation</p>
  </media>

  <p>
    You can resize the ruler to adjust it to the object to measure.
    You can also rotate the ruler in vertical position.
  </p>

  <list>
    <item><p>Resize the ruler by dragging the edges.</p></item>
    <item><p>Change the orientation of the ruler by dragging the corners.</p></item>
  </list>

  <p>To prevent the object to measure from covering the ruler, right click the ruler and select <gui style="menuitem">Always on Top</gui>:</p>

  <media type="image" src="figures/always-on-top.png">
    <p>Use the context menu and select <gui style="menuitem">Always on Top</gui>.</p>
  </media>
